e coverage: build a Manager with ManagerBuilder, register the test extension/context handlers, and exercise EventTestRunnerAdaptor, TestContextHandler, TestInstanceEnricher, and ArquillianResourceTestEnricher with small local test classes and stub ServiceLoader/ResourceProvider implementations.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Without arquillian-core-impl-base, tests may compile against ManagerBuilder but fail at runtime when ManagerImpl is reflectively loaded, or fall back to superficial direct-constructor coverage.\",\n    \"Upstream tests also used Mockito and test-helper classes, but equivalent stubs can be written in generated tests, so those are not deterministic setup requirements.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_06df8aaa6fd994af016a410435daa88194b4922e1f45e44258\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1455, "output": 824, "cacheRead": 24064, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 26343, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782645803823, "responseId": "resp_06df8aaa6fd994af016a41042c67b88194974117a437a613be"}, "toolResults": []}
